<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٧٣٣٧ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5187">قُتَيْبَةُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5348">لَيْثٍ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6509">نَافِعٍ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">ابْنِ عُمَرَ </a><span class="c2">(ح)</span>. وَحَدَّثَنِي <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/549">إِسْحَاقُ، </a>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5027">عِيسَى،</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3564">وَابْنُ إِدْرِيسَ،</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6961">وَابْنُ أَبِي غَنِيَّةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6929">أَبِي حَيَّانَ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3071">الشَّعْبِيِّ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">ابْنِ عُمَرَ </a><span class="special">﵄</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«سَمِعْتُ عُمَرَ عَلَى مِنْبَرِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>